      "name": "Blinding Light",
      "type": "feat",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "The walker sheds bright light in a 20-foot radius and dim light for an additional 20 feet. As a bonus action, the walker can target one creature in its bright light that it can see and force it to succeed on a DC 14 Constitution saving throw or be blinded until the start of the walker's next turn."
        }
